{"tid":1475551,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"《和你飛》原創歌曲","createTime":"2019-08-15T13:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:40:58.000Z","uid":38572,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"77135257a6c7fbe8a99dbfbbfb961da581ef0cc8","tid":1475551,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:50:49.000Z","msg":"好正, 係咁loop, 聽到眼濕濕. 唔知邊個唱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2UltvQ1nkuM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2UltvQ1nkuM&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=ab771f95\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2UltvQ1nkuM</a>"},{"pid":"4bcd2dc01a161f888979b5556ec1d3eb01811dd3","tid":1475551,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc97ec3f3ab95800f6fee8278c1003c228a07ca","tid":1475551,"uid":80024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:13:15.000Z","msg":"好聽<br />\n喺講不出口嘅日子裡 聽歌好治癒<br />\n嗰首這世界若果有暴徒有mv未"},{"pid":"afe22da8b3506c1b4eebbc7ad08a5369c0127559","tid":1475551,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00c4508a9a461f16bee09faf4d5da84c7c41df3","tid":1475551,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"大家支持下原創歌曲啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好淨係留意嗰啲二次填詞作品 <br />\n<br />\n雨傘當年有首 「傘下的人」<br />\n今次有 「和你飛」"},{"pid":"a5331904f90a0908b95466a457a0cba4a0af60fc","tid":1475551,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:17:09.000Z","msg":"《和你飛》<br />\n原創歌曲<br />\n作曲：香港人<br />\n填詞：香港人<br />\n編曲：香港人<br />\n主唱：香港人<br />\n<br />\n聽呼喊聲不絕耳嗎    這心痛怎消化<br />\n難道若說怕    就會停火嗎<br />\n炮火擦身傷勢重嗎    還是強撐嗎<br />\n但怕你    沒法回家<br />\n<br />\n(chorus)<br />\n困於這街道上團聚    卻失散幽暗角落裡<br />\n我不要毅然別去 背城借一 遠方寄居<br />\n有種愛超越限期盛衰    流在我血脈身體裏<br />\n任雨打    任風吹    我也在這裏<br />\n<br />\n那位唱詩拯救我家    看畫面多優雅<br />\n時局在變化    道理有偏差<br />\n痛哭快失聲似啞巴    流淚來記掛<br />\n為了你    奉上白花<br />\n<br />\n(repeat chorus)<br />\n<br />\n仍然堅持    愛縱使不易    難道說我們會休止<br />\n<br />\n已經再一夜未能睡    置身這荒誕歲月裡<br />\n抹乾眼淚行下去    要憑兩手刷新壯舉<br />\n有種愛超越限期盛衰    連繫你我內心交瘁<br />\n暴雨打    狂風吹    與你共進退<br />\n<br />\n舊記憶 歷史中 會有著證據"},{"pid":"6f4abfb96dd9c2880b5ec0114fba9732397be4e7","tid":1475551,"uid":38572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a00c4508a9a461f16bee09faf4d5da84c7c41df3","tid":1475551,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"大家支持下原創歌曲啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好淨係留意嗰啲二次填詞作品 <br />\n<br />\n雨傘當年有首 「傘下的人」<br />\n今次有 「和你飛」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"呢首好正, 睇comment 係素人唱<br />\n對比其他二次填詞, 呢首係超高質, 連埋個MV 真係一流"},{"pid":"bff34634bd103f9372728d0e33c7cf3a9d76bdff","tid":1475551,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4697ed5215ba9bc5f59d707597ef764af4530182","tid":1475551,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:46:54.000Z","msg":"推到出英文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240a5895fde356d30bbe03cbb5e3664addd79024","tid":1475551,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:50:05.000Z","msg":"推到出英文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2daf29b770